{"tid":175132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住 有冇人可以幫到我","createTime":"2017-03-27T09:43:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T10:59:23.000Z","uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"288843aed4b31c39daffc791eabdacb56decaf5f","tid":175132,"uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:43:11.000Z","msg":"失業左兩個月度<br />\n努力搵梗新工<br />\n之前買電話用信用卡分期俾<br />\n每個月還$300幾<br />\n點知今個月真係完全醒唔起要還<br />\n啱啱先收到銀行短訊<br />\n逾期還款$ 900幾<br />\n打去卡中心問先知 原來服務費同罰款加埋要咁多<br />\n佢話可以幫我申請退款，但係要我依兩日交翻$900幾，再即翻俾我<br />\n我想問下依度有冇人可以借到一千俾我，依兩日還左先<br />\n我真係諗唔到方法依兩日交到一千蚊俾銀行<br />\n有諗過問朋友借，但係佢地都讀梗書 都冇能力幫到我<br />\n屋企人依排都煩梗好多野 我更加唔想令佢地擔心<br />\n我知係我蠢唔還卡數   係冇其他辨法下 我只能夠係度問下各位<br />\n能夠借到一千蚊俾我應急嗎<br />\n我可以提供身份證明之類嘅野<br />\n我一搵到新工 出糧就會還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d748f7c0bc89bb4fcd334e5721de94b9a57f6d7b","tid":175132,"uid":46504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"你工都無邊有人敢借比你呀<br />\n問你借都唔敢啦"},{"pid":"a3c12fe30b7e7235e4d8aea49fcc8aecfc8df8d3","tid":175132,"uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:50:50.000Z","msg":"或者 各位有冇d現金出糧嘅工 可以介紹一下俾我 能夠應下急先  麻煩哂各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119a0f80056cdb0c448ee019c859e65b08b42f60","tid":175132,"uid":53036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:51:05.000Z","msg":"咁撚多炒散工你就自己去搵d即pay啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e251dd58b963597b96c2159a1d9d413e2252b6e9","tid":175132,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"即pay 炒散幫到你"},{"pid":"bb11e7e9f233744288ddd9bf879cac2bb87edb8f","tid":175132,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>或者 各位有冇d現金出糧嘅工 可以介紹一下俾我 能夠應下急先  麻煩哂各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒散app大撚把啦"},{"pid":"c2bef815b3964a725c6885c325bbf8f0bfcddce1","tid":175132,"uid":67485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dffabe4cf9dfcd27497beab709c2f74207797ef1","tid":175132,"uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你工都無邊有人敢借比你呀<br />\n問你借都唔敢啦</blockquote><br />\n其實我一路搵梗<br />\nin 左好多地方<br />\n只係一直都等回覆<br />\n因為我係想轉行要冇做之前嗰行<br />\n所以可能d公司未必想請冇經驗嘅新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207893be62ae8ba7aa9a5a184e8e4fa9b963d6bb","tid":175132,"uid":78630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:54:46.000Z","msg":"你有咩skill set 呀"},{"pid":"4c7cbc13a96b1ba88c89fb2d67f4a30b584ce66d","tid":175132,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:54:47.000Z","msg":"賣左部電話"},{"pid":"ee940cb9cc16350c07f481d4e2ab4d413ea2e729","tid":175132,"uid":78630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:55:50.000Z","msg":"你又話佢會退返比你, 咁點解要等你搵到工先還到錢? 唔make sense"},{"pid":"f630c8dc0e628bab25d319a55087d9ab3f932a01","tid":175132,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"咁似騙案"},{"pid":"630391f5f9c798d25c99fd1df45d94646d6a5b29","tid":175132,"uid":51323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"去財仔借"},{"pid":"b60590c636ebc4e026ecb39485c769cac00b2c86","tid":175132,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"賣屎忽"},{"pid":"ea22330a9e7935eec73b4922b358873a76a317ce","tid":175132,"uid":93279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T09:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你又話佢會退返比你, 咁點解要等你搵到工先還到錢? 唔make sense</blockquote><br />\n因為佢退係退落信用卡到 我拎唔翻出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fr