得會有陌生人無啦啦3唔識7借錢俾你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個腦有問題就醫下先啦</blockquote><br />\n又唔好咁講, 我試過on9 借比網友, 之後一去無回頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abb175cb248ba06e1356cfa9415bc34b10a8216","tid":175132,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:12:59.000Z","msg":"$1000問屋企人拎會有幾擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eea2aff302f67597eff7ca8d33efd8b18d5552a","tid":175132,"uid":84508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:13:40.000Z","msg":"幾歲？"},{"pid":"8453142acb43753817aa8816d44f72ea0eff221d","tid":175132,"uid":20989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"屌定你先 咪諗住去財仔借<br />\n以為少少數冇所謂 有得第一次就有第二次<br />\n尤其睇你依家唔經大腦就開post既性格<br />\n後患無窮咪撚亂試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86414f5b6f7a581a31cdfef6b3c5dd448746a20a","tid":175132,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"朋友呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}